        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Fine with me, but can anyone acknowledge why the treesitter highlighter should or shouldn't `flush`? As I see it this adds in a `ui_flush()` that only improves responsiveness as soon as treesitter wants to add highlighting.",
